lg.l:
Be stopt in 
Vials, or transfixt with 
Pins;

The 
Baron now his 
Diamonds pours apace;

Her wrinkled Form in 
Black and 
White array'd;

A Pipkin there like 
Homer's 
Tripod walks;

The 
Bodkin, Comb, and 
Essence to prepare;

But 
Umbriel, hateful 
Gnome! forbears not so;

The 
Bells she gingled, and the 
Whistle blew;
